        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2494373086" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15688509369539028369">Even on a holiday Poirot finds himself in middle of a murder mystery. It appears that it is destined that this Belgian cannot have a peaceful holiday! The plot is brilliant for the way in which the woman is murdered and alibi for the culprit. Unlike other Poirot novels, there are three strong suspects and when at the end with a flourish Poirot unravels the plot and rising to the challenge of the murderer makes him confess, you are left satisfied at the justice delivered. Interesting read</span>

          </span>
